title: Ancient man survived brutal lion attack, suffered lifelong damage: 'Extremely rare'
description: Archaeologists discovered a 6,000-year-old skeleton showing healed lion attack wounds. The ancient man survived the brutal encounter as a teenager and lived for months afterward.

title: Sissu panchayat in Himachal’s Lahaul-Spiti shuts doors to tourists for 40 days to protect ancient traditions
description: Sissu village in Himachal’s Lahaul-Spiti has banned tourists for 40 days from January 20 to February 28 to protect Losar and Halda festival traditions.
